window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The World Fantasy Award-winning thriller about a girl no one can remember, from the acclaimed author of <i>The First Fifteen Lives of Harry August</i> and <i>84K</i>.</p> <p>My name is Hope Arden, and you won't know who I am. But we've met beforeâ€”a thousand times.</p> <p>It started when I was 16 years old. A father forgetting to drive me to school. A mother setting the table for three, not four. A friend who looks at me and sees a stranger.</p> <p>No matter what I do, the words I say, the crimes I commit, you will never remember who I am.</p> <p>That makes my life difficult. It also makes me dangerous.</p> <p><i>The Sudden Appearance of Hope </i>is a riveting and heartbreaking exploration of identity and existence, about a forgotten girl whose story will stay with you forever.</p>"; 
